        <div class="bodysection">
            <div class="body" itemprop="about" data-fieldname="body" data-bind="htmlValue:body"><p>Les Blanks ecstatic paean to the joys
of garlic and all the goodness</p>
<p>it promotes under the sun.  If you were
ever moved by a clove of garlic</p>
<p>come and rejoice.  </p>
<p>Plus Adrin Neatrour's Last Kill (UK 2004;
40 mins) A meditation on the last days of an old itinerant</p>
<p>slaughterer. </p><p><b>Buy Tickets online @ <a href="http://www.wegottickets.com/event/251598">WeGotTickets</a></b></p><p><b><a href="http://www.wegottickets.com/event/251598">  </a></b></p><p><b><a href="http://www.wegottickets.com/event/251598"></a></b></p></div>
