                    </div>

                    <h1 class="domdom">09</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1202">Food Inc.  </a></h1>

                    <h2>9 Jan 2014, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>The film documentary you have to see if
you want to understand the nature of agri-business and the
implications the industrialisation of farming have for our
planet.  Followed by discussion.</p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/1202">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

                </section>
                <section class="row dmod clickable boxb mo0114"
