                    </div>

                    <h1 class="domdom">12</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1204">  The Cook The Thief His Wife And Her Lover (1989)                         </a></h1>

                    <h2>12 Jan 2014, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Perhaps the British Art House movie of the 20th
century. Greenaway probes in outrageous detail the relations of food
to power, sex, revenge and death in its many forms.</p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/1204">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

                </section>
