                    <h1 class="domdom">16</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1205">More Than Honey</a></h1>

                    <h2>16 Jan 2014, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>An extraordinary journey into the
depths of the bee hive, across different cultures, to understand something of the nature of bees and their
importance.  Followed by the chance to talk about and discuss Bees and Honey with local Bee Keepers.   Tickets: £5 and £3.50</p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/1205">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

                </section>
