                    </div>

                    <h1 class="domdom">22</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1301">Nothing Like Chocolate</a></h1>

                    <h2>22 Jan 2014, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>A mythbusting and hopeful exploration of the massive and often highly exploitative cocoa industry. Bhavnani introduces us to Mott Green an anarchist choclatier whose passions encouraged him to start a workers co-op and take on the might of the chocolate industry. Meet NGOs farmers and families facing realities in Cote d'Ivoire including child slave labour and questions like how fair is Fairtrade?</p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/1301">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

                </section>
