                    </div>

                    <h1 class="domdom">23</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1209">Kings Of Pastry</a></h1>

                    <h2>23 Jan 2014, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Pennebaker is best known in the UK for
his Dylan documantary, Don't Look Back.
 Here turns his eyes to pastry chefs competing in France to be King
Patissier. Three days of cream, chocolate
butter and frustration.</p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/1209">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

                </section>
