                    </div>

                    <h1 class="domdom">26</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1208">Tampopo</a></h1>

                    <h2>26 Jan 2014, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>An outrageous spoof on the Samurai
culture which uses the location of Tampopo's noodle bar to introduce
a bizarre gathering of different talents to trigger a series of comic
vignettes whose sole unifying theme is the focus on food.</p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/1208">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

